<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FarmWise Crop Detection</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Custom CSS styles */
        #navbar {
            background-color: #c8e5c9;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */
            align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
            height: 60px; /* Adjust based on your desired height */
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1B5E20; /* Optional: Add a border */
        }

        #logo {
            width: 200px;
            color: green;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        #logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05); /* Slight zoom effect on hover */
        }

        .landing-content {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease;
        }

        .landing-content h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #1B5E20; /* Darker Green */
        }

        .landing-content p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #1B5E20; /* Darker Green */
        }

        .landing-content .btn {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .landing-content .btn:hover {
            background-color: #66BB6A;
            border-color: #66BB6A;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .features {
            background-color: #E8F5E9;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .feature {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .feature h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #1B5E20; /* Darker Green */
        }

        .feature p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #1B5E20; /* Darker Green */
        }

        .feature img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        .footer {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Animation */
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-50px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="background-color: #E8F5E9;color:#1B5E20;">

    <div id="navbar">
        <div id="logo">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">FarmWise</h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing-content">
        <h1>Analyze Crop Health with FarmWise</h1>
        <p>Upload an image of your crops, and we'll help you detect potential diseases or confirm a healthy harvest.</p>
        <a href="login" class="btn">
            Get Started
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">How FarmWise Helps Farmers</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                <div class="feature flex flex-col items-center">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Crop Analysis Icon">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Instant Crop Health Analysis</h2>
                    <p>FarmWise can instantly analyze crop images to determine if they are healthy or show signs of disease.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature flex flex-col items-center">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Disease Detection Icon">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Disease Detection</h2>
                    <p>Our model identifies common crop diseases, providing insights and recommended treatments to help you take action quickly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature flex flex-col items-center">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Freshness Detection Icon">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Fresh Leaf Detection</h2>
                    <p>Upload an image to confirm if your crops are in top condition, ready for harvest or sale.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature flex flex-col items-center">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Farmer Support Icon">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Empowering Farmers</h2>
                    <p>FarmWise helps farmers make informed decisions, improve crop health, and maximize yield.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <p>Contact us:</p>
            <p>Email: info@farmwise.com</p>
            <p>Phone: +1 (123) 456-7890</p>
            <p>Address: 123 Farming Street, AgriCity, Country</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
